{"tid":2345121,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"唔食海鮮/生野 嘅人係咪好奇怪？","createTime":"2020-12-29T09:09:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-29T10:57:21.000Z","uid":344609,"like":2,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9f606b4481d9970b10bf286ece89dff25021eadb","tid":2345121,"uid":344609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T09:09:04.000Z","msg":"我有個朋友由細到大都唔食海鮮或者生嘅嘢<br />\n佢最多淨係食熟嘅海鮮例如三文魚、魚蛋<br />\n叫佢食三文魚呀刺身啊嗰啲 佢就會嘔<br />\n佢又唔係咩宗教信仰或者海鮮敏感 <br />\n佢只不過細細個第一次食 食到佢嘔有陰影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但佢身邊所有朋友都好鍾意食海鮮/日本料理<br />\n得佢一個唔食海鮮算唔算 返社會人格<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e842a3127d1efb240f95a8050bacdf50324a49c","tid":2345121,"uid":32302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T09:10:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/catxm/throw.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2235b008640a6a9bb866cd78b4c587bf317154ed","tid":2345121,"uid":191633,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T09:17:01.000Z","msg":"佢會食到有生理上嘅唔舒服 都唔算怪喇<br />\n<br />\n反而識有啲女仔 <br />\n全部生冷嘢（水果除外）唔食<br />\n中醫話寒涼嘅嘢又唔食<br />\n凍嘢唔飲<br />\n好似係為咗冇肚腩定皮膚好<br />\n我就覺得人生會少好多樂趣咁囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57f419488f01a21ecda20834b72950b1b8079ee3","tid":2345121,"uid":344609,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"2235b008640a6a9bb866cd78b4c587bf317154ed","tid":2345121,"uid":191633,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T09:17:01.000Z","msg":"佢會食到有生理上嘅唔舒服 都唔算怪喇<br />\n<br />\n反而識有啲女仔 <br />\n全部生冷嘢（水果除外）唔食<br />\n中醫話寒涼嘅嘢又唔食<br />\n凍嘢唔飲<br />\n好似係為咗冇肚腩定皮膚好<br />\n我就覺得人生會少好多樂趣咁囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T09:18:29.000Z","msg":"Ching你真係可愛"},{"pid":"76e76ee49a9cf1aa910210f717511ffb3e516b8c","tid":2345121,"uid":217283,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T09:26:30.000Z","ms